full_text:
We often name viruses on their location of origin. 

Ebola
Zika
West Nile
Spanish Flu

That name says nothing about the people who live there.

Thinking a virus name is racist shows who is more concerned with scoring political points than saving lives. https://t.co/b5GIaf3PFt
